                        "content": "The nurse is preparing to measure the apical pulse on an assigned client. The nurse places the diaphragm of the stethoscope over which cardiac site?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "a0f7d178f7b728b8bba7ef20ddeca62d",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Evaluating 评价",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nThe diaphragm of the stethoscope is placed over the skin at the mitral area to listen to the apical pulse. S1 (lub) and S2 (dub) would be distinguished. The pulse would be counted for a full minute. The right atrium, right ventricle, and pulmonic valve areas will not provide clear auscultation of the apical pulse.\n\nClient Needs: Health Promotion and Maintenance\nClinical Judgment/Cognitive Skill(s): Take Action\nCognitive Ability: Applying\nContent Area: Health Assessment/Physical Exam: Heart and Peripheral Vascular\nIntegrated Process: Nursing Process/Assessment\nPriority Concepts: Perfusion, Health Promotion\nStrategies: Subject\n   Test-Taking Strategy:\nFocus on the subject, anatomical area to measure the apical pulse. Use knowledge of anatomy and physiology of the heart. Remember that the best area to measure the apical pulse is the left fifth intercostal space, midclavicular line (mitral area). This will direct you to the correct option.\n \n   ",
                        "id": "3a6a822a94814686b5a7e27d1e80087b",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "8e80528728be416d9606ecc02c1810e8",
                                "content": "An episodic database"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "caaeb51891f64c879dcc73a8063516cc",
                                "content": "A follow-up database"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "ca2ccac0c9ad4162b310cb8a2053fb2a",
                                "content": "An emergency database"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
