                        "type": "0",
                        "version": 0,
                        "content": "A client experiencing \"skipped heartbeats\" is diagnosed with benign premature ventricular contractions and is placed on metoprolol tartrate. The client returns to the primary health care provider's (PHCP's) office 1 month later for a checkup. The nurse would implement which type of database when performing an assessment?",
